urdu transliteration text:
Hai Chaliyan Chaliyan Shaam De Ravan Nu, Behna Dard Sataya.
@HujjatELC
Hai Chaliyan Chaliyan Shaam  - On The Path To Shaam

Veeran Diya Lashan Te Pe Rasiyan Rovan Kaliyan Zahra (Sa) Diya Jaya.
@HujjatELC
Hai Chaliyan Chaliyan Shaam  - On The Path To Shaam

Har Bibi Alvida Ke Key Lash Abbas (As) Te Eh Vehn Keteh. Muk Saray Mahn Geh Ghazi (As) Terey Bajon Chadaran Ah Shimr (La) Ne Laiyan.
@HujjatELC
Hai Chaliyan Chaliyan Shaam  - On The Path To Shaam

Eh Nabi Zadiyan (As) Ne Parday Leh. Moo Lukayan Eh Naal Vahla De. Ismat Diya Paliyan Leh. Sir Mitiyan Ne Paya.
@HujjatELC
Hai Chaliyan Chaliyan Shaam  - On The Path To Shaam

Ah Gay Kehn Hokay Shaam De Vich. Naal Lehkay Beemar Kehdi Nu. Putran Nu Vaar Geya, Nanay De Deen Toon Ehna Chadaran Vi Lutiyan.
@HujjatELC
Hai Chaliyan Chaliyan Shaam  - On The Path To Shaam

Vich Ravan Sakina (Sa) Ro Ro Ke, Neel Ruksar De Vakha Di Eh. Ghazi (As) De Sang Nu Thak Ke Deyn Di Eh Duhayan.
@HujjatELC
Hai Chaliyan Chaliyan Shaam  - On The Path To Shaam

Ahk Da Eh Beemar Ghash Kah Dah. Keevay Akhiyan Chow Khoon Ruk Javey. Puhpiyan Nu Takayan Eh, Darbaran De Vich Khariyan, Hay Naal Sapiyan.
@HujjatELC
